## Composition patterns

### Layout components (do)

```tsx
<Card>
  <Card.Header>...</Card.Header>
  <Card.Body>...</Card.Body>
  <Card.Footer>...</Card.Footer>
</Card>
```

### Layout components (don't)

```tsx
<Card
  header={<div>...</div>}
  body={<div>...</div>}
  footer={<div>...</div>}
/>
```

(The slot-prop pattern is hard to type, hard to style, and invisible in the React tree.)

---

## State

- **Server state** belongs in a data-fetching layer (SWR, React Query, RSC). Never in `useState`.
- **Form state** belongs in a form library (React Hook Form, useActionState). Never hand-rolled.
- **Ephemeral UI state** (open/close, hover) is the only thing that belongs in `useState`.

